txt.en: 'If you enter Ak-ghru to hunt Orcs, bring back trophies of your victories. I would build a wall of Orc-heads to stand as a warning to these vile creatures... what say you?'
'Victory, [placeholder]! I will use these as a warning to the Orcs that their presence will not be tolerated! My thanks to you.'
'I want a wall of Orc-heads before the day is out!'
Orcs serving the White Hand are clear-cutting the forest and shipping the wood off to an unknown location.
Orcs can be found at Ak-ghru.\n\nElfrith asked you to collect Orc-heads as trophies to display as a warning to the Enemy in the Gravenwood.
Elfrith is hiding beyond the bounds of Ak-ghru.\n\nYou should bring the heads you collected to Elfrith.
